com.aurel.track.admin.customize.lists.customOption

Class CustomOptionBaseBL

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.admin.customize.lists.OptionBaseBL
      • com.aurel.track.admin.customize.lists.customOption.CustomOptionBaseBL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListOrOptionBaseBL
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomOptionCascadingSelectBL, CustomOptionSimpleSelectBL, CustomOptionTreeSelectBL

    public abstract class CustomOptionBaseBL
extends OptionBaseBL
    Base class for configuring the lists Contains the methods for configuring the list entries (insert, update, delete etc.) This class abstracts the list type i.e. these methods have the same signature independent of the select type: simple select, tree select, cascading select
